ck\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 20, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vae1665702743322.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vae1665702743322.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vae1665702743322.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vae1665702743322\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"vae1665702743322__middleware_480734\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies the middleware module to use and the path to a Uniface Server host.\n      Mandatory.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"vae1665702743322__topic_d147479e1_d147480e1_d147481e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vae1665702743322__p_d147482e1_d147483e1_d147484e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;init-param&gt;\n &lt;param-name&gt;</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">MIDDLEWARE</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/param-name&gt;\n &lt;param-value&gt;</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">UV8:</code>{<var class=\"keyword varname\">Protocol</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>}<var class=\"keyword varname\">HostID</var>{+<var class=\"keyword varname\">PortNumber</var>}}<code class=\"ph codeph\">|</code>{<var class=\"keyword varname\">User</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">|</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Password</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">|</code>{<var class=\"keyword varname\">UST</var>}\n                        <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/param-value&gt;\n &lt;/init-param&gt;</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vae1665702743322__p_d147485e1_d147486e1_d147487e1\">Default value if omitted: None. This is a mandatory parameter for each Uniface servlet.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vae1665702743322__topic_d106317e1_d106318e1_d106319e1_d106320e1_d106321e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d177783e108\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vae1665702743322__ul_p1s_gsg_xvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vae1665702743322__li_d51188e1_d51189e1_d51190e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">UV8:</code>—Uniface middleware module for connecting to the Uniface\n               Router.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vae1665702743322__li_d51191e1_d51192e1_d51193e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Protocol</var>—network protocol used for the connection; one of\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">TCP</code>or <code class=\"ph codeph\">TLS</code>. Optional; if omitted, the default is\n               TCP.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vae1665702743322__li_d51194e1_d51195e1_d51196e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">HostID</var>—machine where the Uniface Server is installed; can be\n               specified as a host name or as an IP address.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vae1665702743322__li_d51197e1_d51198e1_d51199e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">PortNumber</var>—port number on HostID on which the Uniface Router\n               process is listening. Optional; if omitted, the default is 13001.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vae1665702743322__li_d51200e1_d51201e1_d51202e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">User</var>—user name to start the Uniface Server process; on Windows an\n               optional domain name can be added as a prefix.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vae1665702743322__li_d51203e1_d51204e1_d51205e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Password</var>—password required to start the Uniface Server\n               process.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vae1665702743322__li_d51206e1_d51207e1_d51208e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">UST</var>—UST of the Uniface Server you want to start. Optional; if\n               omitted, the default depends on the Uniface Router.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vae1665702743322__section_q1s_gsg_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d177783e166\">Examples</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vae1665702743322__ul_r1s_gsg_xvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vae1665702743322__li_d51209e1_d51210e1_d51211e1\">No protocol specified, so TCP is used: <p class=\"p\" id=\"vae1665702743322__p_d147494e1_d147495e1_d147496e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">UV8:113.105.399.22|webuser|webpass|wasv</code>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vae1665702743322__li_d51212e1_d51213e1_d51214e1\">TCP protocol is explicitly specified: <p class=\"p\" id=\"vae1665702743322__p_d147497e1_d147498e1_d147499e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">UV8:TCP:113.105.399.22|webuser|webpass|wasv</code>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vae1665702743322__li_d51215e1_d51216e1_d51217e1\">TLS protocol is explicitly specified: <p class=\"p\" id=\"vae1665702743322__p_d147500e1_d147501e1_d147502e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">UV8:TLS:113.105.399.22|webuser|webpass|wasv</code>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yda1665702742322.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>web.xml</a><p>Configuration file of the web application.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ctl1665702541086.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Web Request Dispatcher (WRD)</a><p>The Uniface Web Request Dispatcher (WRD) is used to deploy Uniface web applications. It is a Java servlet that is responsible for brokering requests and maintaining connections between web servers and the Uniface Router. The WRD communicates with the Uniface Server via the Uniface Router.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rnm1665702667413.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>SOAP Request Dispatcher (SRD)</a><p>The Uniface SOAP Request Dispatcher (SRD) is a Java servlet that is responsible for brokering SOAP and WSDL requests for web services.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532926\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532926\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "MIDDLEWARE Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 20, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies the middleware module to use and the path to a Uniface Server host. Mandatory. <init-param> <param-name> MIDDLEWARE </param-name> <param-value> UV8: { Protocol : } HostID {+ PortNumber }} | { User | Password | { UST } </param-value> </init-param> Default value if omitted: None. This is a mandatory parameter for each Uniface servlet. Arguments UV8: —Uniface middleware module for connecting to the Uniface Router. Protocol —network protocol used for the connection; one of TCP or TLS . Optional; if omitted, the default is TCP. HostID —machine where the Uniface Server is installed; can be specified as a host name or as an IP address. PortNumber —port number on HostID on which the Uniface Router process is listening. Optional; if omitted, the default is 13001. User —user name to start the Uniface Server process; on Windows an optional domain name can be added as a prefix. Password —password required to start the Uniface Server process. UST —UST of the Uniface Server you want to start. Optional; if omitted, the default depends on the Uniface Router. Examples No protocol specified, so TCP is used: UV8:113.105.399.22|webuser|webpass|wasv TCP protocol is explicitly specified: UV8:TCP:113.105.399.22|webuser|webpass|wasv TLS protocol is explicitly specified: UV8:TLS:113.105.399.22|webuser|webpass|wasv Related Links web.xml Configuration file of the web application. Web Request Dispatcher (WRD) The Uniface Web Request Dispatcher (WRD) is used to deploy Uniface web applications. It is a Java servlet that is responsible for brokering requests and maintaining connections between web servers and the Uniface Router. The WRD communicates with the Uniface Server via the Uniface Router. SOAP Request Dispatcher (SRD) The Uniface SOAP Request Dispatcher (SRD) is a Java servlet that is responsible for brokering SOAP and WSDL requests for web services. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}